(16986, 12367, 0, 2, 'A Letter to You', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 6, 'The sunlight comes in, the birds are singing\r\nJust let it go, let the morning begin\r\nEverything seems to be so serene\r\nBut why do you still fell upset\r\n\r\nIt’s so sad that you couldn’t get rid of these shitty things\r\nIt’s so sad that you lock yourself in the narrow cage\r\n\r\nYou have to look at the world and, then look at yourself \r\nJust open your hands and see what is in\r\nI’m sure that, you’ll find your smile again\r\n\r\nYou can feel the winds, you can touch the rain\r\nSo forget the scars, and remember the laugh\r\nWell after all things can’t be that bad\r\nJust because you fear to get through\r\n\r\n', '', 179, '', '振中', '振中', '振中', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2009-04-06 01:27:15', '2013-10-07 17:14:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(16987, 12367, 0, 1, 'Destination', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 6, 'Once I tried and tried for this goal\r\nI did \r\nBut I gave up, I screwed up\r\nWhen the night came crushing it all\r\nWill you be there\r\nPlease help me, if you can\r\nI have to try and try for this goal\r\nSomeday\r\nI still hope, I still long\r\nWill the suspense keep what it said\r\nSomeday\r\nThe pain will, disappear\r\n\r\nSay I, that I love you\r\nI can’t live without you, tonight\r\nSay I, that I love you\r\nI can’t breathe without you, tonight\r\n\r\nOnce I tried and tried for this goal\r\nI failed\r\nI felt lost, in this world\r\nBut I think I meet the best dream now\r\nYou’re there\r\nPlease don’t leave, for awhile\r\nI have to try and try for this goal\r\nCause I know\r\nIt’s quite near, it’s right there\r\nCan you hear me cry out this plea\r\nIf you can\r\nJust give me, a sign now\r\n\r\nI’ll find the destination, it’s not so far\r\nCan you come with me? Just tonight (Just you and I tonight)\r\n\r\n', '', 200, '', '振中', '振中', '振中', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2009-04-06 01:34:46', '2013-10-07 17:14:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(16988, 9872, 0, 1, '思念阿母的歌', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 2, 7, 'A1   雄雄唰來放袂記 阿母溫柔的笑面\r\n\r\n     才知影有外久無轉去 陪伴妳 惦身邊\r\n\r\n     人生總有不如意 彼時越頭來離開\r\n\r\n     原諒阮的不得已 乎妳擔心\r\n\r\n     離開這個妳襁養阮的都市 離開妳\r\n\r\nB1   摧著油門 彼時阮的離開\r\n\r\n     妳的慈愛 親像霓虹燈\r\n\r\n     照著我 流浪的暗暝\r\n\r\n     乎阮溫暖 勇敢面對每一日\r\n\r\nSOLO\r\n\r\nA2   天光了後就是暗暝 阮的未來底叨位\r\n\r\n     委屈嘸敢來講出嘴 驚乎妳 傷心\r\n\r\n     妳著愛保重自己 阮的打拼這會有意義\r\n\r\n     阮會提起妳乎阮的勇氣 來認真 過日子\r\n\r\n     期待早一日會凍成功倒轉去 陪伴恁\r\n\r\nB2   攏無怨嘆 愛阮作自己的夢\r\n\r\n     嘸甘著妳 愈來愈白的頭氈\r\n\r\n     每一日 日思夜望的掛念\r\n\r\n     陪伴恁 是阮 尚大的願望\r\n\r\n     ', '', 275, '', 'axom', 'axom', 'axom', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2009-04-06 03:38:32', '2013-10-07 17:14:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
